"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"The US president, after his meeting in Beijing, warned the island against declaring independence formally.\",            \"english_title\": \"US President's Warning\",            \"translated_version\": \"El presidente de Estados Unidos, despu\u00e9s de su reuni\u00f3n en Beijing, advirti\u00f3 a la isla que no declare independencia formalmente.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Advertencia del Presidente de EE.UU.\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Seven people were hurt, two of them seriously, before people nearby chased and stopped the man responsible.\",            \"english_title\": \"Seven People Hurt\",            \"translated_version\": \"Siete personas resultaron heridas, dos de ellas seriamente, antes de que personas cercanas persiguieran y detuvieran al hombre responsable.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Siete Personas Heridas\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Charges might be filed as soon as next week in a case that is reportedly about Cuba's shooting down of two planes in 1996.\",            \"english_title\": \"Charges in Cuba Case\",            \"translated_version\": \"Podr\u00edan presentarse cargos tan pronto como la pr\u00f3xima semana en un caso que se dice es sobre el derribo de dos aviones por Cuba en 1996.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Cargos en Caso de Cuba\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"No group has claimed responsibility for the attacks that have destroyed Mussa town in Borno state.\",            \"english_title\": \"Mussa Town Attacks\",            \"translated_version\": \"Ning\u00fan grupo ha dicho ser responsable de los ataques que han destruido el pueblo de Mussa en el estado de Borno.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Ataques en Pueblo de Mussa\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"President Donald Trump said the operation got rid of Abu-Bilal al-Minuki, who he called the most active terrorist in the world.\",            \"english_title\": \"Operation Against Terrorist\",            \"translated_version\": \"El presidente Donald Trump dijo que la operaci\u00f3n elimin\u00f3 a Abu-Bilal al-Minuki, a quien llam\u00f3 el terrorista m\u00e1s activo del mundo.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Operaci\u00f3n Contra Terrorista\"        }    ]}"